              audio analysis to detect music and voice, transcribe speech, translate, and
              generate captions on which, Natural Language Processing or NLP produces
              additional context. Information present in the media file, the user uploading it,
              the location, user‚Äôs network, history and more - all of this makes this mediatic
              unit computable to the algorithm which gives it a vector ‚Äî that makes it
              circulate, sends it onto the feeds of other ‚Äòusers‚Äô scrolling the platform.
              This is from a machinic point of view. 
